data.description: MUST SEE!!! Beautifully designed and meticulously maintained, sun-lit ranch stye home that has a large rocking chair front porch.  The interior features beautiful hardwood floors, high ceilings and custom detailed walls and trim; oversized Master on the main with sitting room, large master bath and walk in closet.  Enjoy the two-sided fireplace between the large living room and sunroom, overlooking a beautifully landscaped, multi-level backyard that’s perfect for relaxation or entertainment.   Enjoy breakfast in the eat-in kitchen or a family dinner in the separate dining room. The home boasts of a teen/in-law suite upstairs and is situated on a finished basement, with a large bedroom and full bath, music studio / flex space, workshop, and abundant storage.
